head_commit.message:
chore: Merge 2.37 into custom deduplication branch (#8722)

* feat: Add default org unit group set and level for maps [DHIS2-11700] (#8629)

Adds two new methods to the configuration entity and API endpoint:

* POST GET /api/configuration/orgUnitMapDefaultLevel

* POST GET /api/configuration/orgUnitMapDefaultGroupSet

The purpose is to support the new org unit layer in the Maps application by having sensible default selections for org unit level and group set.

(cherry picked from commit 25a0c98d6cf6b963e6926182a9a46d3a187c958a)

* fix: Add org unit profile auth translation (#8633)

Adds org unit profile auth translation. Cleans up response messages for data store API.

(cherry picked from commit 949a472be902787776f4fc41bc36c9f221100bfa)

* fix: Make data store response messages more succinct (#8637)


(cherry picked from commit c9df2a9122192a9ac5bad9f0aacb6f054a7fd203)

* fix: Data Element formName not shown in the forms (#8624)

Co-authored-by: Stian Sandvold <stian@dhis2.org>

* feat: Add skip analytics to prog stage data element [DHIS2-11720] (#8635)

Adds boolean skip analytics property to program stage data element entity. Skips data elements with this property enabled in event analytics table generation.

(cherry picked from commit d78d7a0ad414f1152b388603893e089d4c023514)

* fix: Rename facility configuration properties [DHIS2-11700] (#8643)


(cherry picked from commit 8071279755a3f8330e52fe9ca32acb853dfff8a9)

* build: Use resetWar wrapper with intance existance check (#8654)

* fix: Logic for dashboard of type APP [DHIS2-11739] (#8670)

* fix: Invalid data statistics snapshot date [DHIS2-11047] (#8671)

Co-authored-by: Lars Helge Øverland <lars@dhis2.org>

* fix: Bump rule-engine version to fix error text (#8658)

Co-authored-by: Lars Helge Øverland <lars@dhis2.org>

* feat: Add data view max org unit level to user restriction [DHIS2-11737] (#8660)

This patch is about introducing a new association from the user entity to organisation unit level to represent a "Data output max organisation unit level".

(cherry picked from commit bf0f4455bcfb111f335ae8ed05b66d896bda8d31)

* chore: say goodbye to PT (#8677)

BREAKING CHANGE: pivot tables app unbundled

* fix: Line list and pivot table (enrollment) do not give the same total [2.37-DHIS2-11524-patch.2] - backport (#8662)

* backporting

* backporting

Co-authored-by: Stian Sandvold <stian@dhis2.org>

* fix: sharing is not saved when create new ProgramStage (#8688)

* fix: data value import - delete with zero or no value [DHIS2-11624] (#8610)

Takes care of three cases:
* delete by updating to zero should work
* delete by using strategy DELETE with no value or the old value should work
* delete by using strategy DELETE with new value different to the old one should work (did work before but now is tested as well)

* refactor: Improve naming for dimension item keywords [DHIS2-11760] (#8697)

* Renames DimensionalKeywords to DimensionItemKeywords which is a more appropriate name.
* Rename method addGroupBy to addKeyword, as these keywords have nothing to do with group by operations.
* Makes getKeywordsreturn an immutable list to make the class immutable.
* Uses singleQuote over wrap.
* Remove unsafe varargs use in tests.
* Removed "Default" prefix from two test class names as we want to test interfaces not implementations.
* Adds Javadoc.

(cherry picked from commit 994f3978970e9c8f9e11d2b339e1ccb9f8de7d33)

* fix: Simplify event analytics org unit where clause logic [DHIS2-11760] (#8705)

Simplifies the where clause for organisation units for event analytics SQL queries. The query planner has already split org units with different org unit levels into separate queries, so no need to group by org unit level again in the analytics service. Preserves the use of in operator instead of many or clauses.

(cherry picked from commit b3198cca7f0b774bb55c78c150a4d701297981e3)

* chore: Remove mobile web module (#8679)


(cherry picked from commit a966b0a9850827aa5fd605aed843109fa9e23610)

* fix: Add org unit level column to event/enrollment tables [DHIS2-11760] (#8706)

Adds an oulevel column to event and enrollment analytics tables. Renames the aggregate analytics table level column to oulevel.

(cherry picked from commit 874a77b27a631eeb68b6de251ae67947083ea36a)

* chore: Make tokens unusable when 2FA is enabled (#8657)


(cherry picked from commit 69339cdec3528632b6a7be595adabbcae8e223c1)

* ci: make the name of the log artifact more explicit (#8674)


(cherry picked from commit b5bfd212ed2ac642f642412348d2eba72e7cc9eb)

* fix: Add annotations for auditing relationships; Special case for RelationshipItem when getting attributes (#8691) (#8700)

(cherry picked from commit 4e2f605ef29591f5921cb4c1b29ab61c3c328834)
